{"tid":2006742,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"大家睇JOJO邊幕會睇到哭能咗?","createTime":"2020-05-08T03:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T15:29:44.000Z","uid":227967,"like":85,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"43db5468666d5b4806d734e2efc3fd650f7a99b1","tid":2006742,"uid":227967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:52:45.000Z","msg":"第2代:<br />\ncae~~~~~~~~~sar~~~~~~~~~~~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />JOJO這是我最後的波紋了！你收下吧！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1nETUdK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1nETUdK.jpg&h=dd90eaad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第3代:<br />\n伊奇戰死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身似為佢好閪, 結果突然大爆發犧牲咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QA3A7t4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQA3A7t4.jpg&h=dd37a2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n花京院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />十七年的孤獨 五十日的友情....等咗17年遇到知己但之後就死咗....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0eTxqfT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0eTxqfT.jpg&h=71b6a050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第4代:<br />\n億泰個怪物老豆拎住張相喊, 睇到好心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3zQbXC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3zQbXC.jpg&h=54aafe56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仗助屌早泄廢....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後早泄諗計令到個仔對佢改觀, 見到早泄老到咁又開始有啲痴呆....諗返佢全盛時期...個對比好令人心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2iBnNwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2iBnNwx.jpg&h=239e630c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肥仔, 雖然佢幾仆街, 但本性都唔算太壞, 佢都算有一顆正義的心, 見佢死都咁慘都哭了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最慘係好似好多人都當佢唔存在咁, 可能真係your face your fate....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ikKMuK6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FikKMuK6.jpg&h=cd276fa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 最近入坑JOJO, 睇到第四代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e23b669d7a356104a9d7a16e23cf6b58d88652","tid":2006742,"uid":177089,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:57:17.000Z","msg":"Boss俾人輪迴個幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341876d4c474dad30fc69f197035873afb1457a6","tid":2006742,"uid":229794,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:5