cf3","tid":2006742,"uid":34409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e635956425f7c883958a897f0c41b6cc536ef946","tid":2006742,"uid":43613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f619ccdee788114d9baf606d85b672ac2e3b0fac","tid":2006742,"uid":183066,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WyrvdRg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWyrvdRg.jpg&h=aa79406a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iumK2KZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiumK2KZ.jpg&h=675dd8ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n石之海啲人話好垃圾<br />\n但係我真係睇到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n荒木寫死主角都唔係新鮮事<br />\n不過第六部啲劇情真係麻麻<br />\n睇多幾次又覺得其實冇啲人講到咁差"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:25:29.000Z","msg":"agger, 第六部翻睇一次, 真心唔差"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"第六部係中段拖得太長，搞到故事好似冇左重心咁。<br />\n其實第七部都有類似問題，只係佢主線係跑馬賽事，<br />\n你會冇咁覺眼。<br />\n<br />\n呢d 問題你一次過睇唔覺的，但追連載既話就會好覺眼。<br />\n例如我係追單行本(所以屋企有過百本jojo)，<br />\n第六部果時隔幾個月買一本，但感覺係整個故事冇推進過，<br />\n再加上第六部既畫風凌亂(呢點第八部明顯線條簡化左)，<br />\n部份替身能力又好難明白(風水龍個能力我果時睇到一頭冒水)。<br />\n所以先咁多人覺得第六部唔好睇。"},{"pid":"6cb0710c88f7ccab60dbabb893f893f5b86bf1f5","tid":2006742,"uid":22917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6e23b669d7a356104a9d7a16e23cf6b58d88652","tid":2006742,"uid":177089,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:57:17.000Z","msg":"Boss俾人輪迴個幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T21:50:11.000Z","msg":"仲死緊"},{"pid":"ba2c57071c50d330dc6bb8430600fc7dfcb18520","tid":2006742,"uid":22917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62ac5b0e892d1db068b5e4fcc4ac933eeaa80ee1","tid":2006742,"uid":36461,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:03:2